#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn13.7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn13.7:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 13 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 13 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Abhisamayavagga "
msgstr "1. Comprehension "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn13.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Samuddasutta "
msgstr "7. The Ocean "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn13.7:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.7:1.2"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso mahāsamuddato dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni uddhareyya. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose a man was to draw up two or three drops of water from the ocean. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.7:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn13.7:1.4"
msgid "katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ, yāni vā dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni ubbhatāni yaṃ vā mahāsamudde udakan”ti? "
msgstr "Which is more: the two or three drops drawn out or the water in the ocean?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.137, sc2
msgctxt "sn13.7:2.1"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ, yadidaṃ mahāsamudde udakaṃ; "
msgstr "“Sir, the water in the ocean is certainly more. "

msgctxt "sn13.7:2.2"
msgid "appamattakāni dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni ubbhatāni. "
msgstr "The two or three drops drawn out are tiny. "

msgctxt "sn13.7:2.3"
msgid "Neva satimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na sahassimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na satasahassimaṃ kalaṃ upenti mahāsamudde udakaṃ upanidhāya dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni ubbhatānī”ti. "
msgstr "Compared to the water in the ocean, it’s not nearly a hundredth, a thousandth, or a hundred thousandth part.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.7:2.4"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave … pe … "
msgstr "“In the same way, for a noble disciple, the suffering that’s over and done with is more …” "

msgctxt "sn13.7:2.5"
msgid "dhammacakkhupaṭilābho”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn13.7:2.6"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
